title: karma > [[id:0a6dcf44-6c2c-432a-90a7-babfbb3e0b7d][justice]]
pid: ab791cbb-ee4d-4653-a281-b8601435e017
body: |2-
  There can be (always, one hopes) karma where no justice.
  The way it feels, to who, and the strange resulting inequality,
  the biggest winners having the hollowest existences,
  those with the fullest often not recognizing it,
  the search for a just accounting demanding an unreasonable persistence of inter-character masses.
